---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<PageLayout 
  title="iNNv0 - Start Innovating Yesterday" 
  description="Innovation management framework for early-stage organizations. Save time and accelerate your innovation journey with AI-powered tools and proven methodologies."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero 
    title="Start Innovating Yesterday"
    subtitle="With iNNv0, you'll save time and accelerate your innovation journey. We've meticulously crafted the tools and methodologies that will enable you to take the first steps in implementing an innovation management system much faster."
  />
  
  <!-- Value Proposition -->
  <section id="learn-more" class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We focus on identifying and implementing innovation opportunities that deliver 
          <span class="gradient-text font-semibold">high value with minimal resources</span>, 
          ensuring innovation is accessible and practical. While we won't help you win the most disruptive 
          innovation award of the year, we <strong>will help you start working and developing your company's 
          innovation capacity</strong> by implementing pragmatic, simple innovation management processes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Framework Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          Early Stage Innovation Management <span class="gradient-text">Framework</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          A comprehensive approach to building innovation capacity through strategic design and tactical execution.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Design Dimension -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal">
          <div class="glass-card p-8 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <i class="fas fa-compass text-2xl text-white"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Design</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              This dimension focuses on establishing the strategic foundations for innovation, 
              aligning efforts with the company's vision and overall goals.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 transition-all">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900">Maturity Assessment and Prioritization</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  A focused diagnosis to determine the organization's current state of maturity in innovation management.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Tool: assessmeNNt</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 transition-all">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900">Organization Description</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  A concise analysis of the current business model, basic organizational culture, and key capabilities.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Tool: organizatioNN</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary-300 transition-all">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900">Innovation Management Planning</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  Creation of a simple, actionable strategic roadmap to elevate the organization's innovation maturity level.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600">Tool: plaNN</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Execution Dimension -->
        <div class="scroll-reveal">
          <div class="glass-card p-8 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500 to-secondary-700 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket text-2xl text-white"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Execution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              Once the initial strategy is defined, this dimension focuses on the implementation, 
              management, and optimization of daily innovation activities.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-secondary-300 transition-all">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900">Program Design</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  This involves the tactical structuring of initial programs that will drive innovation.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-secondary-600">Tool: desigNN</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-secondary-300 transition-all">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900">Opportunity Management</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  This is the systematic process for feeding the innovation engine, focusing on identifying 
                  obvious and easily accessible opportunities.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-secondary-600">Tool: opportuNNities</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-secondary-300 transition-all">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900">Initiative Management</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
                  This focuses on the agile tracking and development of selected opportunities, 
                  turning them into concrete projects.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-secondary-600">Tool: iNNitiatives</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- AI Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
            Leveraging <span class="gradient-text">AI</span> for Your First Steps
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            Starting to innovate can seem daunting, but Artificial Intelligence offers surprisingly 
            accessible tools to take those initial steps with confidence and effectiveness.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-grid">
          <Card 
            title="Fast, Personalized Diagnostics"
            description="AI-powered assessment forms conduct quick and accurate diagnosis of your organization's maturity level in innovation management."
            icon="fa-chart-line"
          />
          
          <Card 
            title="Data-Driven Opportunities"
            description="AI processes large volumes of data to identify patterns and trends, pinpointing high-value, low-risk innovation opportunities."
            icon="fa-database"
          />
          
          <Card 
            title="AI-Assisted Ideation"
            description="AI tools act as tireless brainstormers, generating novel ideas and offering fresh perspectives to accelerate your ideation process."
            icon="fa-brain"
          />
          
          <Card 
            title="Process Optimization"
            description="Identify inefficiencies and suggest optimizations, automating repetitive tasks so your team can focus on strategic activities."
            icon="fa-cogs"
          />
          
          <Card 
            title="Reduced Learning Curve"
            description="AI personalizes educational content and offers interactive tutorials, acting as a virtual coach guiding you step-by-step."
            icon="fa-graduation-cap"
          />
          
          <Card 
            title="Cost-Effective Solutions"
            description="Our deep integration of AI allows us to offer services at substantially lower costs while maintaining high quality."
            icon="fa-dollar-sign"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-accent-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Key Benefits</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center scroll-reveal">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-bullseye text-3xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Clarity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">A defined path eradicates confusion and aligns teams.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center scroll-reveal">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500 to-secondary-700 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-bolt text-3xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Speed</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Jump from zero to prototype in weeks, not months.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center scroll-reveal">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-700 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-3xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Risk Mitigation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Test assumptions early to reduce costly missteps.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center scroll-reveal">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-accent-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-users text-3xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Empowerment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Builds capability through guided autonomy and learning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-900 text-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center scroll-reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          Ready to Start Innovating?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Innovation doesn't have to be complicated. We're here to ensure your organization 
          can take meaningful steps towards a more innovative futureâ€”starting today.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
            Get Started Now
          </a>
          <a href="/framework" class="btn-secondary">
            Explore Framework
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
